专注面条 - 学霸学习计时器

platformAttributes.ios.subtitle.k: 助你放下手機，打敗分心
助你放下手机，打败分心

platformAttributes.ios.editorialNotes.st.k: Focus Noodles is not your ordinary focus timer. Once you’ve set a time and gathered all your digital ingredients, place your phone face down to start and let your dish cook. When you lift your phone at any point, steam escapes—halting the cooking process. (Nobody likes undercooked noodles, right?). Focus Noodles’ delightful details add fun to your productivity sessions, and with enough hard work and determination, you might even earn the title of noodle master!
透過有趣得意的細節助你提昇效率。只要展現十足拼勁和決心，你或有可能奪得「麵條大師」頭銜！
这是一款令人“垂涎”的专注 App。只要有足够的努力和决心，你就可以赢得面点大师的称号！
提升專注力也可以很好玩！善用這款專注計時器，你除了能更堅定意志投入當下工作，還有機會獲得麵點大師的稱號喔！
Égayez vos sessions productives avec ces délicieux détails. Vos efforts et votre détermination pourraient même vous faire remporter le titre de maître des nouilles !
Delightful details add fun to your productivity sessions, and with enough hard work and determination, you might even earn the title of noodle master!
